sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Benutzer
    participant System as System
    participant Encryption as Verschlüsselung

    User->>System: Initiate Video Call
    System->>Encryption: Encrypt Video Stream
    Encryption-->>System: Encrypted Video Stream
    System-->>User: Start Video Call with Encrypted Stream
    User->>System: Send Video Data
    System->>Encryption: Encrypt Video Data
    Encryption-->>System: Encrypted Video Data
    System-->>User: Transmit Encrypted Video Data
    User->>System: End Video Call
    System-->>Encryption: Terminate Encryption
    Encryption-->>System: Encryption Terminated
    System-->>User: Video Call Ended